description:
Gemini did a solo the day before. The video was fine, but I had mic problems on two cameras.
And the Serviced video actually had one mic problem, not too much to overcome, so he jumps right into the oral position.
Gemini is 19, seems to like more mature guys, and this Serviced video was extra fun cuz he was into it from the start. He's not shy about exploring and touching, so it was good on my self-esteem as well.
He's got a big bone as well, so if you like 'em super sized, he's a good guy for ya!
title: Bryan & Gemini - Serviced
